Licence: intended AGPL-3.0-or-later.

This project reads and replays the oref/OpenAPS controller as used by AAPS and Trio,
which sits in an AGPL-licensed ecosystem. AGPL-3.0-or-later is therefore the intended
licence, and is likely required if any oref logic is vendored.

